<h1> Midwinter </h1>
<p><i>Published on: <time datetime="2024-07-16T11:05:30.482Z">July 16, 2024</time></i></p>
    
       <a href="/posts/tag/posts">#posts</a>
    
       <a href="/posts/tag/poetry">#poetry</a>
    
</br>
<p>Fresh frost has visited overnight,<br>
morning shudders, barely starts<br>
Our fallow fields now writhe with blight.<br>
Fresh frost has visited overnight,<br>
We have lost colour from our sight-<br>
like fools, we hold hope in our hearts.<br>
Fresh frost has visited overnight,<br>
morning shudders, barely starts.</p>

</br>
